  <brief_title>Safety and Efficacy Study of the Z-Lig Medical Device Compared to Allograft</brief_title>
  <acronym>Z-Lig</acronym>
  <official_title>A Prospective, Randomized, Double-Blind, Multicenter Clinical Trial to Evaluate the Safety and Efficacy of the Z-Lig Medical Device Compared to Allograft for the Reconstruction of Ruptured Anterior Cruciate Ligaments</official_title>
  <sponsors>
